": \"patriotism\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 225}, {\"ngram\": \"memories\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"a childhood\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being asked about early sporting memories often leaves a sense of complete and utter embarrassment.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"early sporting memories\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"complete and utter embarrassment\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now 24, I do not vividly remember the 2003 Rugby World Cup or the then \\\"clean\\\" dominance of Lance Armstrong on the Tour de France.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8183656053372133e-41, \"text\": \"Lance Armstrong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9992657264372027, \"rank\": 0.0007329625857995612, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2003 Rugby World Cup\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"the then \\\"clean\\\" dominance\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My first rugby memory is one of tears - returning home from Twickenham after my Premiership side were spanked at HQ - while England not qualifying for the Euros 16 years ago and the 2005 Ashes are just about in the memory bank.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.or