, {\"ngram\": \"City AM's sports desk\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because early in the morning I'd wake up, run downstairs, and watch sport until mid-afternoon.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"mid\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"afternoon\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day for two weeks that was my life.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two weeks\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And what was this paradise of sporting action, where athletics was followed by badminton, canoeing and gymnastics?\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this paradise\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting action\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"badminton\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The quadrennial event really is a highlight of a sporting cycle, up there with the Fifa World Cup and rugby's equivalent.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.997687076914355, \"rank\": 0.002134560998053767, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The quadrennial event\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"a highlight\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"a sporting cycle\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a display of patriotism, where you'd support anyone and everyone as long as they had the words \\\"Team GB\\\" or \\\"Great Britain\\\" slapped across their kit.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a display\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"patriotism\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Team GB\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Great Britain\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"their kit\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The splendour of the opening ceremony in all of its regimented glory and the emotion I'd never thought I'd see from archers, triathletes and weightlifters.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The splendour\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"its regimented glory\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotion\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"archers\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"triathletes\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"weightlifters\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a sporting awakening.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sporting awakening\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And since then - in the three Olympiads that have followed in London, Rio de Janeiro and Tokyo - the Olympic Games have continued to captivate my attention.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1857, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://d