aris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"this week\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the splendour\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"gravitas\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"this fortnight\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"dreams\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up since Beijing the politics, drama and grossness that comes with these types of events has shown itself.\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999976740128, \"rank\": 2.3259671684548492e-08, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the politics\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"drama\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"grossness\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"these types\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have seen doping scandals, athletes denied access to the Games because of their biology and problems with poor attendances.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doping scandals\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"their biology\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2351}, {\"ngram\": \"poor attendances\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But back in Europe for the first time since London - really one of the greatest ever Games - the Olympics will shine for a British audience once again.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2420, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999984252099, \"rank\": 1.558584656751588e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8470732693969634, \"rank\": 0.1804010517143402, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest ever Games\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB won 51 medals in Beijing.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999577085, \"rank\": 2.4530171813908574e-11, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2554, \"end\": 2561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999976740128, \"rank\": 2.3259671684548492e-08, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"51 medals\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I probably watched them all at some point that summer.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In London it was 65, Rio saw a return of 67 and in Tokyo it was 64.\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2621, \"end\": 2627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999984252099, \"rank\": 1.558584656751588e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2639, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999942265276, \"rank\": 5.77357393036569e-09, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999990363744569, \"rank\": 9.635705145925736e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a return\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our stock has risen and expectations are higher now than 16 years ago.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our stock\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in a world where there is sport on every single day the Olympics, for me, remains the one.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2794}, {\"ngram\": \"every single day\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the singular event where I cancel plans to watch the shooting, delay a dinner to see the 5,000m, and ignore my family until the open water swimming has concluded.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the singular event\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"the shooting\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"a dinner\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5,000m\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2955}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"the open water swimming\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics, and our success in it, makes me proud to be British; and it makes me wonder just how there are people who do not like any sport at all.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"our success\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"any sport\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My Olympic memories have been good ones; Chris Hoy, Super Saturday, the Brownlee Brothers and Bethany Shriever.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3247, \"end\": 3255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"score\": 0.9986061752430788, \"rank\": 0.001394395849217471, \"text\": \"Brownlee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\"}, {\"begin\": 3256, \"end\": 3264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"score\": 0.9999998944258606, \"rank\": 9.932593607207109e-08, \"text\": \"Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\"}, {\"begin\": 3269, \"end\": 3285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bethany Shriever\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My Olympic memories\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3194}, {\"ngram\": \"good ones\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's probably why it's an event of joy in my psyche.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3320}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"my psyche\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But even if that was not the case I'd be tuning in every day from this Friday.\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"this Friday\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot wait to get lost in rugby sevens, skateboarding and climbing.\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot wait to shout at the swimming relays, the surfing and race walk.\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the swimming relays\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Games, in all of its politicised glory, remains the greatest show on Earth.\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3586}, {\"ngram\": \"its politicised glory\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3619}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest show\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3646}, {\"ngram\": \"Earth\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is undeniable.\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this article\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"the City AM newsletter\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"our top stories\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3802}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3820}, {\"ngram\": \"latest updates\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3839}]}]}"